dialogue.add("YOU","There\'s a note here.");
dialogue.add("ROMANTIC","Greetings from another bunker!");
dialogue.add("ROMANTIC","If you\'re reading this, be relieved in knowing that we\'re not completely alone down here.");
dialogue.add("ROMANTIC","The system they\'ve established here seems quite backwards, keeping us all siloed away from each other.");
dialogue.add("ROMANTIC","Yet, it\'s also quite romantic, isn\'t it?");
dialogue.add("ROMANTIC","Alone, waiting out the end of the world, with other lonely hearts just a wall or two away...");
dialogue.add("ROMANTIC","(unless you\'re one of the lucky ones who got a roommate or two (although, that situation could be quite romantic as well)).");
dialogue.add("ROMANTIC","Since this letter has found you, I imagine there may be some way of contacting other bunkers. If so, then I kindly ask you to write back whenever you can.");
dialogue.add("ROMANTIC","The sounds of the clock & air vent make for terrible company, & there\'s nothing romantic about eating preserved meats from a crate.");
dialogue.add("ROMANTIC","I hope to hear from you soon.");
dialogue.add("ROMANTIC","Sincerely, a Solitary Heart");

